od;\n                    dp[x][i+j][1][0]%=mod;\n                    dp[x][i+j][1][1]+=(1ll*tmp[i][1][0]*((dp[v][j][1][0]+dp[v][j][1][1])%mod)%mod+1ll*tmp[i][1][1]*((1ll*dp[v][j][0][0]+1ll*dp[v][j][0][1]+1ll*dp[v][j][1][0]+1ll*dp[v][j][1][1])%mod)%mod)%mod;\n                    dp[x][i+j][1][1]%=mod;\n                }\n            }\n            siz[x]+=siz[v];\n        }\n    }\n}\nint main()\n{\n    scanf(\"%d%d\",&n,&k);\n    for(int i=1;i<n;i++)\n    {\n        int u,v;\n        scanf(\"%d%d\",&u,&v);\n        mp[u].push_back(v);\n        mp[v].push_back(u);\n    }\n    dfs(1);\n    printf(\"%d\",(dp[1][k][0][1]+dp[1][k][1][1])%mod);\n    return 0;\n}", "_detail_requested": true, "_cached_at": "2026-06-05 15:31:20"}